Text: Special Notice to Our Valued Net SAAver Email Subscriberstoday we extended an invitation for you to renew your free subscription to the American Airlines Net SAAver email program We apologize that due to high demand you may not have been able to access AAcom today for subscription renewal Since we are unable to meet demand at this time we request that you renew your subscription at a later date Please rest assured that your current subscription is valid and will not be canceled without another opportunity to renew If you were successful in renewing your subscription earlier today please excuse this notice Thank you and we apologize The AAcom Web Team Subscribe Unsubscribe Instructions This email has been sent to MTAYLOECTENRONCOM If you choose not to receive Net SAAver Fares messages or if you would like to change your email address please visit dataMTAYLOECTENRONCOMKeyCmXbBCDhQvv or email us with a subject of unsubscribe and well remove you from all American Airlines email lists including Net SAAver International Net SAAver and ALL other American Airlines email programs There may be a short delay if you choose to resubscribe Please include this ENTIRE message in your reply MessageId
